reviewText: this two parter has two different stories. the first is about a guy that goes to work early only to find his supervisor masturbating at his work station. his is later punished by that supervisor and made to stay late at work to fix a problem. she ends up tricking him in to having sex with her. and next story is about a boy who's older  sisters find out that he had sex with his girlfriend in a public place and as a punishment one of them jerks him off with her foot and ties him up in a tree, later the other sister has sex with him.
